data.description: MUST SEE FOR YOURSELF!!!  21.7 acres of open pastured and mixed woods with a 2 story brick home that is gorgeous!!  4 bedrooms, 3 bath, 4,000 +- heated and cooled.  2 fireplaces one wood burning the other is gas logs.  A saltwater swimming pool with a shop and 2 stocked ponds!!  A huge sunroom with a full kitchen that overlooks the pool and a chain linked fenced backyard!!  The backside of the lands borders the National Forest. Look no further because this a dream home not far from Forest but in the country!!!
